@HostAddress = http://localhost:18001
@Token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ==========================================
### 1. AUTHENTICATION MODULE
### ==========================================

### Mapeado em LoginEndpoint, RegisterEndpoint, RefreshTokenEndpoint, SetupMfaEndpoint, VerifyMfaEndpoint

### Register User
POST {{HostAddress}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

###

### Login User
POST {{HostAddress}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

###

### Refresh Token
POST {{HostAddress}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "your_refresh_token_here"
}

###

### Setup MFA (Requires Auth)
POST {{HostAddress}}/auth/mfa/setup
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

###

### Verify MFA (Requires Auth)
POST {{HostAddress}}/auth/mfa/verify
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

{
  "code": "123456"
}

### ==========================================
### 2. USERS MODULE
### ==========================================

### Get User Profile (Requires Auth)
GET {{HostAddress}}/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

###

### Update User Profile (Requires Auth)
PUT {{HostAddress}}/users/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

{
  "name": "Eduardo Weise",
  "phoneNumber": "+5511999999999"
}

###

### Soft Delete User Profile (Requires Auth)
DELETE {{HostAddress}}/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}


### ==========================================
### 3. SERVICES MODULE
### ==========================================

### Get All Services
GET {{HostAddress}}/services

###

### Get Service By ID
@ServiceId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
GET {{HostAddress}}/services/{{ServiceId}}

###

### Manage Client Service Duration (Requires Auth - Should be Admin/Staff, but requires Auth only now)
POST {{HostAddress}}/services/{{ServiceId}}/client-duration
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

{
  "clientId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "durationMinutes": 45
}


### ==========================================
### 4. SCHEDULING MODULE
### ==========================================

### Get Available Slots
GET {{HostAddress}}/appointments/available-slots?date=2026-10-15&serviceId={{ServiceId}}

###

### Book Appointment (Requires Auth)
POST {{HostAddress}}/appointments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

{
  "serviceId": "{{ServiceId}}",
  "startTime": "2026-10-15T14:30:00Z"
}

###

### Get Appointments - Client (future, no date)
GET {{HostAddress}}/appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

###

### Get Appointments - Admin/Manager by date
GET {{HostAddress}}/appointments?date=2026-10-15
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

###

### Cancel Appointment (Requires Auth)
@AppointmentId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
POST {{HostAddress}}/appointments/{{AppointmentId}}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}


### --- SWAP REQUESTS ---

### Create Swap Request (Requires Auth)
POST {{HostAddress}}/appointments/swaps
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

{
  "requesterAppointmentId": "{{AppointmentId}}",
  "targetAppointmentId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111"
}

###

### Accept Swap Request (Requires Auth)
@SwapRequestId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
POST {{HostAddress}}/appointments/swaps/{{SwapRequestId}}/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

###

### Decline Swap Request (Requires Auth)
POST {{HostAddress}}/appointments/swaps/{{SwapRequestId}}/decline
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}


### ==========================================
### 5. PAYMENTS MODULE
### ==========================================

### Get Debt Balances (Requires Auth)
GET {{HostAddress}}/payments/debts
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}

###

### Pay Debt Balance (Requires Auth)
@DebtId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
POST {{HostAddress}}/payments/debts/{{DebtId}}/pay
Authorization: Bearer {{Token}}
